OL,3,CPolice remain at the scene after three
OL,4,Crelatives found dead in family home
OL,6,FPolice remain at the scene after three
OL,7,Ffamily members were found dead in Co
OL,8,FAntrim.
OL,10,FA murder investigation was launched
OL,11,Fafter the three were found dead in a
OL,12,Ffamily home in Ballymena on Monday
OL,13,Fmorning.
OL,15,FUTV understands a young girl is one of
OL,16,Fthree family members alongside a man
OL,17,Fand woman.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
