OL,3,CPolice remain at the scene after three
OL,4,Crelatives found dead in family home
OL,6,FPolice confirmed that the three people
OL,7,Fwere related and found inside the
OL,8,Fproperty, adding there was no "ongoing
OL,9,Frisk" to the public and officers were
OL,10,Fnot seeking anyone else in relation to
OL,11,Fthe deaths.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday morning police tape
OL,14,Fremained outside the property on the
OL,15,FOld Cullybackey Road.
OL,17,FToys could be seen outside the house
OL,18,Fand a pair of pink and blue child's
OL,19,Fsandals were drying on a washing line.
