PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784038719
OL,3,CPolice remain at the scene after three
OL,4,Crelatives found dead in family home
OL,6,FMid and East Antrim District
OL,7,FCommander, Superintendent William
OL,8,FCalderwood, said the bodies of a male
OL,9,Fand two females were discovered at the
OL,10,Fhome at around 9am on Monday.
OL,12,F"The cause of death has not yet been
OL,13,Fformally established and post-mortem
OL,14,Fexaminations will take place in due
OL,15,Fcourse," he said.
OL,17,F"As such, it would be inappropriate to
OL,18,Fcomment further at this time, and I
OL,19,Fwould ask that the public avoid
OL,20,Fspeculation."
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@HO]yD@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
