PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784038719
OL,3,CPolice remain at the scene after three
OL,4,Crelatives found dead in family home
OL,6,FHe added: "However, I want to reassure
OL,7,Fthe public that we do not believe that
OL,8,Fthere is any ongoing risk, and at this
OL,9,Fstage we are not seeking anyone else
OL,10,Fin relation to the deaths."
OL,12,FMayor of Mid and East Antrim Thomas
OL,13,FGordon said the "heart-breaking"
OL,14,Fincident has "shocked the local
OL,15,Fcommunity and left many people
OL,16,Fstruggling to come to terms with the
OL,17,Fdevastating news".
OL,19,FHe added: "I extend my heartfelt
OL,20,Fcondolences to the family and friends
OL,21,Fof those who have lost their lives.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@[O]uD@QOUuD@`O]vD@NOUyD@QO]{D@
