OL,3,CPolice remain at the scene after three
OL,4,Crelatives found dead in family home
OL,6,F"My thoughts and prayers are with
OL,7,Feveryone affected by this tragedy
OL,8,Fduring what will be an unimaginably
OL,9,Fdifficult time.
OL,11,F"As investigations continue, I would
OL,12,Furge anyone who may have information
OL,13,Fthat could assist the investigation to
OL,14,Fcontact the police. I would also like
OL,15,Fto thank the emergency services and
OL,16,Fall those involved in responding to
OL,17,Fthis tragic incident.
OL,19,F"I will be keeping the family and all
OL,20,Fthose impacted in my thoughts and
OL,21,Fprayers in the days and weeks ahead."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU{D@AOU}D@eO]
